<v Speaker 2>Bailaran.

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:05.720
<v Speaker 1>Bailaran.

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:08.120
<v Speaker 1>A new informal.

00:05:08.120 --> 00:05:09.080
<v Speaker 2>Bailaras.

