<v Speaker 1>Bailaras.

00:05:10.280 --> 00:05:10.919
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:05:10.919 --> 00:05:14.280
<v Speaker 1>So we get the future tense without having to learn anything new.

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:18.360
<v Speaker 1>We just have to remember that we can look back at Aber.

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:24.880
<v Speaker 1>and see what the different versions of a bear were and then use them to build our future.

